OL,5, Manchester Arena bomb survivors have   
OL,6, filed landmark legal action against a  
OL,7, conspiracy theorist who claims the     
OL,8, attack was faked.                      
OL,10,FMartin and Eve Hibbert, who were left  
OL,11,Fwith severe disabilities after the 2017
OL,12,Fblast, are suing Richard D Hall for    
OL,13,Fdefamation and harassment.             
OL,15,FIt is the first time such action has   
OL,16,Fbeen launched in the UK against a      
OL,17,Fconspiracy theorist.                   
OL,19,FMr Hall did not respond to the BBC's   
OL,20,Frequest for comment.                   
